                                    class="card-img-top" alt="Blog post image">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <span class="badge bg-info mb-2">Travel Tips</span>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">10 Essential Items for Your Next Trip</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Don't forget these crucial items when packing for your next
