                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560448204-e02f11c3d0e2?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80"
                                    class="card-img-top" alt="Blog post image">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark mb-2">Hosting Tips</span>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">How to Become a Superhost</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Learn the strategies that successful hosts use to earn top
